JACKSON, Miss. The Mount
Vernon Missionary Baptist
Church, organized more than 80
years ago was destroyed by fire
last week.


1t was the second Negro church
burned In the area in the last
two weeks. Officials suspect
arson.


A total of 10 Negro churches
have been set Attire in the state
since the summer voter regis
tration program began.


No arrests have been made
in connection with the fires.
